made for Sphere.55R4.0.2 by Moe
With this script your players can harvest different kinds of wood on different trees. The tree is tested from statics, so you won't get walnut logs from a cedar. To use it simply put it into your script directory and make sure it loads after sphere_region.scp (where default mr_tree is located).

known bugs:
Some leaves (i_foliage_cedar2, i_foliage_oak, i_foliage_oak_fall, i_foliage_oak2, i_foliage_oak2_fall) are t_tree in the default scripts. This can mess up lumberjacking. Set them to t_foliage as they should be.
Yew tree (i_tree_yew_1) is t_normal in default scripts. Set it to t_tree to harvest logs from it.


